    <h1>Best practice: Linking characteristics to attributes</h1><div id="preamble">
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="admonitionblock tip">
<table>
<tbody><tr>
<td class="icon">
<i class="fa icon-tip" title="Tip"></i>
</td>
<td class="content">
14/4/2021: real.de becomes Kaufland.de
</td>
</tr>
