</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>A new column is added to the product.csv afterwards.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p><strong><em>Note:</em></strong> If two characteristics have the same name, then the characteristic with the lower ID will be overwritten. This way you can overwrite attributes which already exist by default (EAN, name etc.).</p>
</div>
